    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried clearing the variables but a part of the memory still seems to be 'stolen' by the process and doesnt come back. it's like there's something small and persistent taking up space in the background. how can i track down exactly what is holding onto those resources?",
      "source": "evaluator"
